Targets:

clean - remove generated files and build directory

html - Generate a html version of the document
pdf - Generate a pdf version of the document
kindle - attempt to generate a kindle version of the document
wc - clean and do a word count

verify - create a trivially encrypted version for use with nano-wrimo

view - view an html version of the document
viewpdf - view a pdf version of the document

init - copy templates from the Scrivener submodule into the main project
